data.title: Liberty County Texas
data.text:
EFFECTIVE OCTOBER 1, 2022, THE LIBERTY COUNTY TAX ASSESSOR / COLLECTOR will be collecting the property taxes for Dayton ISD as it does for Liberty County, City of Dayton and various other entities. You will receive one bill for your property taxes instead of two bills like you have in the past.

The property tax information and history will be available through the Liberty County Tax Office after October 1, 2022. For your convenience, you can access the information and make payments via the following options:
